cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper deals with video interpolation, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method uses a deep neural network architecture (cs.LG) and involves predicting multiple frames between non-consecutive frames (cs.AI). The paper also reports results on two benchmarks related to video processing (cs.MM) and uses a joint loss function and adversarial loss for training (cs.NE).
